## CONTENT GUIDELINES

### SEO Title (`seo.title`)
- Format: "[Product Name] [Year] | [Main Keyword/Benefit]"
- Example: "Red French Tip Santa Nails 2025 | Christmas Press-On Nails"
- Max 60 characters
- Include primary keyword
- Make it clickable and benefit-focused

### Meta Description (`seo.description`)
- Format: "[Benefit statement]. [Key Feature]. [Unique Angle]. [CTA]"
- 155-160 characters exactly
- Include long-tail keyword naturally
- Include a number or specific detail (e.g., "7-14 days," "24 pieces")
- End with CTA: "Shop now," "Discover," "Get yours"
- Example: "Premium red French tip press-on nails with Santa hat designs. Salon-quality Christmas nails that last 7-14 days. Easy application, festive style. Shop now on Amazon."

### Keywords Array (`seo.keywords`)
- 8-10 keywords total
- Mix: 2 main keywords + 3 long-tail keywords + 2 topical keywords + 1-2 user voice search phrases
- Example: ["christmas nails", "santa press-on nails", "red french tip nails", "holiday nail designs", "festive press-on nails", "christmas nail art", "santa hat nails", "winter press-on nails"]
- NO keyword stuffing
- Each keyword should be unique and relevant

### Full Description (`fullDescription.html`)
- 300-400 words minimum
- Structure: Hook → Benefits → Features → Materials/Durability → Use Cases → Closing
- Use semantic HTML: `<p>`, `<strong>`, `<em>` tags
- Start with emotion-based hook (e.g., "Transform your holiday look...")
- Include specific numbers and details (24 pieces, 7-14 days, 10-15 minutes)
- Address pain points (e.g., "Unlike traditional polish that chips and fades...")
- Mention target audience explicitly (e.g., "Perfect for busy women...")
- Each product must have COMPLETELY UNIQUE content - no generic descriptions
- Write as persuasive copy, not a dry specification sheet

### Specifications (`specifications`)
- Include standard fields: packageContents, material, finish, durability, applicationTime, reusable, sizes
- Add 2-3 product-specific fields relevant to this item
- Examples: colorOptions, waterproof, hypoallergenic, vegan, crueltyFree, lightweight, temperature-resistant
- All values should be concise strings or numbers

### FAQs (`faqs`)
- 4-5 questions minimum
- Questions should reflect real customer searches and objections
- Answer should be 2-3 sentences, specific and helpful
- Include keywords naturally (not forced)
- Cover: durability, reusability, application, sizing/fit, care instructions
- Example format:
  ```
  {
    "question": "How long do these Christmas press-on nails last?",
    "answer": "These premium press-on nails last 7-14 days with proper application using the included nail glue. For shorter wear (1-3 days), you can use the adhesive tabs instead."
  }
  ```

### Related Products (`relatedProducts`)
- Array of 5 product IDs that complement or are similar to current product
- These should make sense for cross-selling
- Example: If product 1 is red nails, include other red products, Christmas products, or complementary nail styles

### Internal Links (`internalLinks`)
- Blog: Link to a blog post about this product category/trend (should exist or be planned)
- Inspo: Link to inspiration/gallery page showing this style
- Topic: Link to a broader topic/guide page
- Each should have: title, slug, image path, and excerpt/description

